<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB08226</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT ESTABLISHING AND INSTITUTIONALIZING LONG-TERM CARE FOR SENIOR CITIZENS, PROVIDING FUNDS THEREFOR AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Aims to provide a National Long-Term Care Program Framework for the Senior Citizens that shall endeavor to help them in improving their total well-being and their full participation in society.

Intends to grant affordable and quality services to the elderly that will alleviate their difficulties.
